Lets you search via voice for your favorite song on Youtube! 

However there are countless issues to fix or even things that you can add:

Short list of further improvements:

  1. Since its gonna be used in a car, weather information could be useful
  2. Youtube script uses the first video that is on that list; Im not sure if selecting only songs/music videos is an option
  3. Keep in mind, it uses Google Speech Recognition -> limited to 50 words a day, however I have never encountered such an limit
  
  
